was using Carrillo.

19
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:47,645
And we know how that ended, right?

20
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:52,681
So, you're taking a break
from burning down villages?

21
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:57,761
What we do is fill in
for an absent government.

22
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:02,721
We're going to kill everyone
close to Escobar one by one.

23
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:06,486
Until he's alone. With nothing.

24
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:10,206
[Fidel]
What we want, Mr. Pefia,

25
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:14,046
is to make Escobar understand
he is not untouchable.

26
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,963
We want him to be afraid.

27
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,444
There's just one small problem.

28
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,811
Just one?

29
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:28,041
To catch him, we need the satellite
technology and surveillance

30
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,122
that your government has, Agent Pefia.

31
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:34,687
And I'm just going to...
hand that over to you?

32
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:38,202
We have been partners for a while now,
Agent Pena.

33
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,805
All the information that he gave to you,
I gave to him.

34
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:48,210
We are simply making...
a small adjustment.

35
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,964
Thanks for the drink.

36
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,769
Too much stupidity for my liking.

37
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:30,365
The Castafios can be useful.

38
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,125
