39
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,325
Yes, Javier.

40
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,011
I'm a narco.

41
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:43,645
And I believe in honor and loyalty,
like you.

42
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,210
[door opens]

43
