gathering intel.</i>

79
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:18,370
<i>The brass was still
reviewing and approving it.</i>

80
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,721
<i>And it was still finding its way to us.</i>

81
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,686
<i>But, shit, man...</i>

82
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,765
<i>you can have all the intelligence
in the world,</i>

83
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:32,003
<i>but if nobody's there to act on it,
what's it worth?</i>

84
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,801
<i>Nothing.</i>

85
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:42,051
<i>All it adds up to
is</i> a <i>growing stack of unread files</i>

86
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:44,009
<i>on</i> a <i>dead man's desk.</i>

87
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:48,127
<i>We were back where we started: nowhere.</i>

88
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:51,170
- [upbeat Latin music plays on radio]
- [in Spanish] Look, Dad.

89
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,287
